  - mission critical

** What provides Oracle

  - comprehensive technologies pre-integrated in the software stack

** Concepts

  - active-passive
  - active-active
  - failover
  - I/O fencing

  - shared nothing architecture
  - shared disk and cache architecture

** Products

*** RAC

  - easy to deploy and manage
  - load balancing out of the box

  - clusterware
  - interconnect
  - asm
  - virtual internet protocol
  - extended distance cluster < ~100km

  - recoverability
  - error detection
  - continous operations

**** Retail

  - Retail batch job processing needs a huge server
  - Parallel query and DML (but this should be supported by the
